videos.description: Rasir Bolton navigates through defenders then takes flight to punish the rim on a vicious one-handed dunk for Iowa State.

videos.description: CJ Fredrick drives and tosses a lob pass to Jack Nunge who goes up to flush a dunk down with two hands for Iowa.
